}{\f1 \fs20 \b \cf1 *177}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1  E. The Fundamental Interior Attribution Error (or, Getting Ourselves Wrong) }{\*\bkmkstart Document1zzSDUNumber58}\f1 \fs20 {\*\bkmkend Document1zzSDUNumber58}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1 }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1     We all wear glasses that carry a date in time and the name of some geographic area, and with even the keenest of vision these glasses allow us to see only limited distances and partial motion of our world.}\par 
