 cue from its intentions and its immediate environment.  Such cues can influence what we think about next." }{\*\bkmkstart Document1zzFN_B467}\f1 \fs20 {\*\bkmkend Document1zzFN_B467}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1 }{\field {\*\fldinst {HYPERLINK \\l Document1zzFN_F467 }}{\fldrslt {\f1 \fs20 \ul \cf2 [FN467]}}}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1   Such is the starting point for one influential marketing guide promising to "demystif[y] the effects of advertising and describ[e] some of the psychological mechanisms underlying them . . . written primarily for those who foot the bill for advertising and those who produce advertising." }{\*\bkmkstart Document1zzFN_B468}\f1 \fs20 {\*\bkmkend Document1zzFN_B468}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1 }{\field {\*\fldinst {HYPERLINK \\l Document1zzFN_F468 }}{\fldrslt {\f1 \fs20 \ul \cf2 [FN468]}}}{\f1 \fs20 \cf1 }\par 
