\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   He dreads no famine, in unfruitful years; }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   If harvests fail from inauspicious skies, }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   The Master's providence his food supplies; }\par 
