\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   The cabin home, not comfortless, though rude, }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   Light daily labour, and abundant food, }\par 
