\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   The cheerful song, that rings in every field, }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   The long, loud laugh, that freemen seldom share, }\par 
\pard \qj \fi0 \li0 \ri0 {\f1 \fs20 \cf1   Heaven's boon to bosoms unapproached by care, }\par 
